<plot>Bedlam explores the psyche of Robert Peyton, a thirty-something family/businessman who witnessed the death of his daughter. Plagued with the visions of her murder, he struggles to keep his job, his marriage and his sanity intact while running from her killer. It's a journey deep into the mind of a man fighting for his sanity, running for his life and spiraling deeper into Bedlam.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062980</url></doc>
